def insert_before_character(string):
    return string.replace('a', 'Wa')

print(insert_before_character("banana"))  # bWananWa
print(insert_before_character("watermelon"))  # Wwatermelon
print(insert_before_character("apple"))  # Wapple
print(insert_before_character(""))  # ""
